708022f-b.title: Manhattan: 3rd Avenue - 21st Street (East)
708022f-b.text:
(1)
Third Ave., east side, north from, but not including East 21st
Street, showing the Third Ave. Elevated Line, and its 23rd Street station.
Also seen (in the background), is the tower of the Chrysler Building.
Note the Christmas trees displayed on the sidewalk.
December 23, 1936.
P. L. Sperr.
11O REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)
The same, from a point several feet southward. The restaurant
shown on the extreme right, is ''Beefsteak John's''.
December 23, 1936.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(3)
A view of No. 265 Third Ave., adjoining the N.E. corner of East
21st Street, showing the restaurant mentioned in No. 2.
August 5, 1937.
L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
